  <bioghist id="aspace_ea39a020286df63caa8f4415048d4f77">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Gavras was one of the four original Finger Lakes Runners Club members listed on the club charter. He was a competitive masters runner who competed on a Finger Lakes Runners Club masters team all over the United States and in Europe and continued to run into his 80's.</p>  </bioghist>
